    {
      "key": "0f1d5ece-6c5d-4aa2-91ba-64a91dd83bbe",
      "position": 1,
      "properties": {
        "description": "<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Display**: Show “Reflect” slide\n\n&nbsp\n\n**Reflect:**\n- *Draw a puzzle that would use a nested loop.* \n\n- *Try coding the solution to your own puzzle.*",
        "name": "Reflection"
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "0f1d5ece-6c5d-4aa2-91ba-64a91dd83bbe",
        "lesson_activity.key": "ee8736b6-9de1-4ea4-b7b2-45e53507aee3"
      }
    },
    {
      "key": "a5fee35e-7353-4539-bc9b-a12d8829afbb",
      "position": 1,
      "properties": {
        "description": "<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Display**: Show “Reflect” slide\n\n**Reflect:** _We use the word “if” to make sure that some action only occurs when it is supposed to._\n\n_Finish this statement: \nIf I do well in my classes, then...._\n",
        "name": "Reflect"
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "a5fee35e-7353-4539-bc9b-a12d8829afbb",
        "lesson_activity.key": "0479757c-ca4f-44e9-a0b3-2cc2b8630f26"
      }
    },
    {
      "key": "f7b65699-e5f7-44d3-b550-8edac6250db3",
      "position": 2,
      "properties": {
        "description": "<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Display**: Show “Vocabulary” slide\n\n- **Conditionals** - Statements that only run under certain conditions.\n\n- **Pseudocode** - A plain language description of the steps in an algorithm.",
        "name": "Vocabulary"
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "f7b65699-e5f7-44d3-b550-8edac6250db3",
