    {
      "key": "6970adb9-8d55-4fe0-a104-cb78fdf5fc62",
      "position": 1,
      "properties": {
        "description": "<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Display**: Show “Reflect” slide\n\n**Reflect:** \n *Draw a scene where someone is using a conditional. \nHow does this scene demonstrate a conditional?*\n\n",
