    {
      "key": "438bcb00-d9e7-4cdc-a144-6f320790bf53",
      "position": 1,
      "properties": {
        "description": "\n<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Display**: Show “Reflect” slide\n\n\n**Reflect:** *Give an example of a puzzle where you would use a while loop, but not use a repeat loop. Can you give an example of a puzzle where you would use a repeat loop, but not a while loop?*",
        "name": "Reflection"
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "438bcb00-d9e7-4cdc-a144-6f320790bf53",
        "lesson_activity.key": "c5ee0e3a-6dd7-4171-a119-7377a3f3a42d"
      }
    },
    {
      "key": "eaaeb1ad-1c34-4ee5-9274-3984a10da250",
      "position": 1,
      "properties": {
        "description": "In this lesson, students will be creating loops that only run \"until\" a condition is true.  Help the students understand how this works by leading them in group activities and having them do an action \"until\" some condition is true.  For example: Have students touch their nose \"until\" you tell them to stop.",
        "name": "Introduction\r"
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "eaaeb1ad-1c34-4ee5-9274-3984a10da250",
        "lesson_activity.key": "b546bcdf-bcca-4e5b-91c4-370d0f895a54"
      }
    },
    {
      "key": "252a4d0e-6b26-43cc-b715-75062d439a09",
      "position": 2,
      "properties": {
        "description": "<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Display**: Show “Reflect” slide\n\n**Reflect:** *Describe a time when you repeated an action until some condition was true.*\n\n&nbsp\n\n####Preview of Online Puzzles \n\n&nbsp\n\n<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Display**: Show “Preview - Until Loops in Maze” slide.\n\n&nbsp\nPull up a puzzle from today's Code Studio puzzles. We recommend Puzzle 4. \n\n - Ask the class what the bird should repeat to get to the pig.\n    - The bird should repeat \"move forward\", \"turn right\", \"move forward\", and then \"turn left\".\n - Ask the class what they can use to repeat this code. \n    - The bird should repeat this pattern *until* it reaches the pig. \n\nFill in the rest of the code using the \"repeat until\" loop and press \"Run\". Discuss with the class why this worked."
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "252a4d0e-6b26-43cc-b715-75062d439a09",
        "lesson_activity.key": "b546bcdf-bcca-4e5b-91c4-370d0f895a54"
      }
    },
    {
      "key": "3c95f8cb-fc5a-4079-a88f-b28ccc032278",
      "position": 3,
      "properties": {
        "description": "\n###Vocabulary\n\n&nbsp\n<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Display**: Show “Vocabulary” slide\n\n\n- **Condition** - Something a program checks to see if it is true before allowing an action.\n\n- **Conditionals** - Statements that only run under certain conditions.\n\n- **Loop** - The action of doing something over and over again.\n\n&nbsp\n\n<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Display**: Show “Vocabulary (continued)” slide\n\n- **Repeat** - To do something again.\n\n- **Until** - A command that tells you to do something only up to the point that something becomes true.\n"
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "3c95f8cb-fc5a-4079-a88f-b28ccc032278",
        "lesson_activity.key": "b546bcdf-bcca-4e5b-91c4-370d0f895a54"
      }
    },
    {
      "key": "079f0184-1571-41fb-87b7-32a860ec2c26",
      "position": 1,
      "properties": {
        "description": "####Online Puzzles\n\nBringing together concepts is not easy, but this set of lessons is meant to help students  see the endless possibilities of coding when using conditions. If students struggle at all with understanding the similarities or differences between \"while\" loops and \"until\" loops, have them try to think of how they would use similar statements in their real lives.\n\n&nbsp\n\n<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Display**: Show “Level 1 - Skill Building” slide\n",
        "name": "Until Loops in Maze",
        "progression_name": "Skill Building"
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "079f0184-1571-41fb-87b7-32a860ec2c26",
        "lesson_activity.key": "7d70f80b-922d-4bee-8182-075209bcb340"
      }
    },
    {
